OL,3,CBorders orchestra celebrates 50th
OL,4,Canniversary with year of special events
OL,6,FPeebles orchestra was set up in 1976
OL,7,Fby Claire Garnett MBE who moved to
OL,8,Farea and realised there was no local
OL,9,Fgroup to play with.
OL,11,FShe said she 'had a dream' that she
OL,12,Fcould form an orchestra in the town,
OL,13,Fand she did. She took it from strength
OL,14,Fto strength for 42 years before
OL,15,Fhanding over the reigns.
OL,17,FShe was later awarded an MBE for
OL,18,Fservices to music in the community in
OL,19,Fthe Borders.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
