OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1779639072
OL,3,CBorders orchestra celebrates 50th
OL,4,Canniversary with year of special events
OL,6,FOver the decades, the orchestra has
OL,7,Fproduced a number of international
OL,8,Fmusicians and helped shape the lives
OL,9,Fand careers of many who've been part
OL,10,Fof it.
OL,12,FIts youth orchestra, which is no
OL,13,Flonger running, also nurtured the
OL,14,Ftalent of hundreds of local
OL,15,Fyoungsters. One of them is Colin
OL,16,FScobie who is now an internationally
OL,17,Facclaimed violin soloist, and he's
OL,18,Freturned to take part the 50th
OL,19,Fanniversary celebrations this weekend.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
