PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1779639072
OL,3,CBorders orchestra celebrates 50th
OL,4,Canniversary with year of special events
OL,6,FOn Saturday 23 May, they held a
OL,7,Fspecial jubilee concert in Peebles in
OL,8,Fwhich Scobie played Brahms violin
OL,9,Fconcerto.
OL,11,FAnd exhibition detailing the history
OL,12,Fof the group also opened to the public.
OL,14,FThey're both part of a programme of
OL,15,Fspecial events planned to take place
OL,16,Fthroughout the year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
