PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1779639072
OL,3,CBorders orchestra celebrates 50th
OL,4,Canniversary with year of special events
OL,6,FIn February, they held an 'orchestra
OL,7,Ffor all' event which was a chance for
OL,8,Fanyone who plays an instrument to
OL,9,Fexperience playing in an orchestra. It
OL,10,Fwelcomed musicians from ages 6 up to
OL,11,F80.
OL,13,FTwo further major concerts are planned
OL,14,Ffor September and November.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/4
